code: public static TlsVersion forJavaName(String javaName) {     switch(javaName) {         case "TLSv1.3":             return TLS_1_3.         case "TLSv1.2":             return TLS_1_2.         case "TLSv1.1":             return TLS_1_1.         case "TLSv1":             return TLS_1_0.         case "SSLv3":             return SSL_3_0.     }     throw new IllegalArgumentException("Unexpected TLS version: " + javaName). }

static List<TlsVersion> forJavaNames(String... tlsVersions) {     List<TlsVersion> result = new ArrayList<>(tlsVersions.length).     for (String tlsVersion : tlsVersions) {         result.add(forJavaName(tlsVersion)).     }     return Collections.unmodifiableList(result). }
